{"tid":1438390,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聽日去大埔把撚咩 班大埔人根本唔想你哋入去","createTime":"2019-08-09T18:05:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T03:45:16.000Z","uid":227929,"like":5,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"912c779bd4b662bb42b99ead4e02c65977462525","tid":1438390,"uid":227929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T18:05:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔好意思做標題黨呃咗各位入嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />利申非分化,但聽日區外人(尤其勇武)入大埔真係好危險<br />\n如果你已經知道大埔好危險,加埋有心理準備畀和理非阻你行動嘅,咁我唔阻你<br />\n否則,請花少少時間睇<br />\n <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">三大原因:</span></span><br />\n <br />\n<ins>1. 地型問題</ins><br />\n <br />\n可能你會話「元朗地型都柒啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />啲人咪又去!」 錯! 大埔地型絕對危險同易圍堵好多! 之前都有巴打講過, 引用番個舊Post :<br />\n(【極危險】義士可能被大圍捕) <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1434969/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1434969/page/1</a><br />\n <br />\n805唔封地鐵站係因為<strong>警力分散</strong>同<strong>街坊相對和平</strong>, 但聽日只有大埔一區遊行, 而且大大個新界北狗屋總部喺度, 要包圍大肆拘捕話咁易。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <br />\n <br />\n<ins>2. 大埔主力和理非新手, 前線欠缺支援</ins><br />\n <br />\n805大埔前線手足會明我所講, 大埔街坊係極度和理非同新手&hellip;連最簡單嘅抗爭手勢呀開遮呀乜都唔識, 就算支援都係橋上或屋苑平台鬧幾句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />同黃大仙街坊勇武支援程度冇得比。千幾個街坊不敵幾十隻防暴，真係畀啲狗指住嚟笑。<br />\n <br />\n唔好話我分化<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />睇睇以下證據:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BPpdRUp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBPpdRUp.jpg&h=11d01767&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n再聽聽805前線講法:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rLK5Jhb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrLK5Jhb.jpg&h=9da90cd3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hVo6sJS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhVo6sJS.jpg&h=5427fc6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大埔街坊又點睇?<br />\n- 好多人仲覺得810可以+想真正和理非遊行<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uOK108s.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuOK108s.png&h=abc2d4d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n- 有唔少人覺得805勇武係騎劫咗和平集會<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9AQkxfE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9AQkxfE.png&h=3209b9c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n以為佢地齌搞和理非,唔需要勇武? 唔係喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 搞手話要,但純粹利用勇武保護街坊同用血汗喚醒未覺醒嘅中間派<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>大埔人,問心,咁樣唔自私咩?</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kaqXzuH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkaqXzuH.png&h=e416b0b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n個人好唔希望見到和理非阻礙勇武事件發生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但當連805行出馬路都會俾人阻嘅時侯, 分化嘅情景好可能喺聽日發生<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ronu93M.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fronu93M.png&h=7575073b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n805街坊支援唔到前線,聽日你覺得會唔會呢？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EHCKYXG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEHCKYXG.png&h=17f0192f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n <br />\n3. 搞手問題<br />\n <br />\n利申我由一開始都好支持搞遊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />初初仲有份鬧啲隊搞手嘅人.但班搞手愈來愈過份, 包括:<br />\n <br />\n- 同勇武割蓆<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2THfmba.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2THfmba.jpg&h=12f67294&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qRmcopx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqRmcopx.jpg&h=9b39ef03&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲撐警,仲有搞手話希望遊行可以令市民睇到狗有克制嘅一面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n <br />\n <br />\n原本仲想出張咁嘅文宣&hellip;.<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vXx7b1m.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvXx7b1m.jpg&h=903bb414&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n由一開始講想真和理非遊行,承諾文宣會強調和理非同大埔地型危險叫勇武手足慎重考慮, 又話805有咩事嘅話會取消810遊行,結果係一樣都冇做過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出爾反爾<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mdzxoap.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMdzxoap.jpg&h=208f0213&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Rvbsb3L.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRvbsb3L.jpg&h=96ff212c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後文宣有冇喺呢方面著墨? 大家都有眼見<br />\n啲人問圍堵問題,搞手答會提供2-3條撤離小路, 但堅持遊行12個鐘前先公佈,因為啲狗會佈唔切防<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你地根本由頭到尾都冇考慮過外區手足死活<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jfouqDt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjfouqDt.jpg&h=c21ecae6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有,點解805大埔開戰嗰晚,你班文宣會得閒夜晚出sticker,班物資又得閒去開會?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />做冷氣軍師帶頭搞遊行真係合適咩?<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C014ewZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC014ewZ.jpg&h=1fca470e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n <br />\n再重申 如果外區手足(不論勇武或和理非)明白大埔嘅危險性,加埋有心理準備畀和理非阻你行動嘅,咁我唔阻你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n各位大埔人, 令你地唔開心嘅話好抱歉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />想叫停大埔停遊行,唔係因為驚,而係戰略問題。當一個地方地型差, 街坊又支援唔到, 係咪要冒高風險堅持? 我地已經送咗五百幾個頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />慎重啲諗清楚啦<br />\n好多大埔人到依刻都仲覺得 行完散水=be water=散水=冇事, 無視過往次次衝突係由狗咬人先的起源。我地成日講嘅be water, 唔係講散水, 而係示威者點行如流水,撚到班狗捉摸唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <br />\n在下愚見, 係和理非嘅, 聽日拉大隊去機場參觀<br />\n勇武手足, 你地可以分散喺其他區行街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又或者抖返日備戰星期日勇武手足, 你地可以分散喺其他區行街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又或者抖返日備戰星期日</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你睇下admin都同勇武割席 仲要連撐警呢啲嘢都做得出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 死咗佢好過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n成班自私撚分明就係想要勇武幫佢哋做人肉盾牌擋催淚彈擋子彈 爭取時間返屋企<br />\n<br />\n你哋自己衡量下值唔值得入去大埔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我睇到真係好嬲 希望佢哋快啲畀黑警大大巴大巴摑醒<br />\n<br />\n利申：照幫其他區嘅和理非<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSources:<br />\n[多圖] 810大埔極有可能重演何式凝大量送頭事件<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1438151\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1438151</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"af34022e23d3f28a3252659e4adcb4d072308791","tid":1438390,"uid":51064,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T18:07:21.000Z","msg":"會去機場既手足！<br />\n可以叫旅客follow ig @freehk_ <br />\n入面有唔同既英文文宣！可以俾佢地搭車睇同之後繼續follow up 香港既新聞！！！！！"},{"pid":"3d851811b48e9b08a8ed30bd43a888b285215b7e","tid":1438390,"uid":227929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T18:07:29.000Z","msg":"利申： 不分化 但係真係好嬲<br />\n各位手足衡量下入唔入去好<br />\n可能佢哋第時畀黑警大大巴大巴摑醒咗之後又會出咗一批勇武手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbfbc7a4f8b22202c42bc22acc1e385f47296321","tid":1438390,"uid":248404,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T18:08:10.000Z","msg":"咪分化帶風向啦仆街"},{"pid":"64af759714004c8539a02282c3c842cadd5f8413","tid":1438390,"uid":227929,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"dbfbc7a4f8b22202c42bc22acc1e385f47296321","tid":1438390,"uid":248404,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T18:08:10.000Z","msg":"咪分化帶風向啦仆街"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T18:08:34.000Z","msg":"撚有分化<br />\n你睇下佢點樣對我哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38c9de27e5c0fd65fc764114a75707dca6805708","tid":1438390,"uid":184746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dbfbc7a4f8b22202c42bc22acc1e385f47296321","tid":1438390,"uid":248404,"like":3,"disl